          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The total photon absorption cross sections",
                " were measured using two identical magnetic Compton",
                " spectrometers, one of which served as a",
                " normalization instrument but second served as",
                " instrument for measurement of the attenuation of",
                " the photon beam.",
                "In order to obtain the nuclear photoabsorption",
                " cross sections  from the measured",
                " cross sections calculated values for non-nuclear",
                " cross sections (essentially the Compton effect",
                " and pair production) were subtracted."
              ]
            }
          ],
